<% job = @job %>

<div class="min-h-screen">
  <%= render "home/shared/header",
    bg_color: "dark-gray",
    text_color: "white",
    title: job[:title],
    description: "#{job[:type]}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#{job[:location]}",
    no_border: true,
    gap: "gap-4 md:gap-6"
  %>

  <div class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Gumroad is a profitable, independent, and venture-debt-free tool for creators. We've paid out over $600M. Now, we're growing a high-density team in Dumbo to reclaim our spot as the #1 creator economy tool. To get there, our core engine the path from a customer's "Buy" button to a creator's bank account must be the most reliable and frictionless infrastructure on the internet.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What you'll do</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          You will own the integrity of the Gumroad economy. We process millions of dollars a week across every time zone. Your job is to ensure that code is fast, math is perfect, and money moves without fail.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
          <% job[:responsibilities]&.each do |item| %>
            <li class="text-lg"><strong><%= item[:title] %>:</strong> <%= item[:description] %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">The stack</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">We ship with tools that work.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <% job[:stack]&.each do |item| %>
            <li class="text-lg"><strong><%= item[:name] %>:</strong> <%= item[:tech] %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What we offer</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          We are a high-output team of builders. We don't have an HR department, we don't have "middle managers," and we don't do corporate side quests.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="text-lg"><strong><%= job[:salary] %>/year + bonus + equity + benefits</strong></li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>30-Hour week:</strong> We expect 30 hours of deep focus. The other 138 hours of your week are yours.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>Dumbo HQ:</strong> We work from 20 Jay St. We sync in person when things are hard because it's faster to turn a chair than to send a Slack.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>Lunch and coffee:</strong> We cover your food and coffee on the days you're in the office.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>The setup:</strong> A stipend for your home office plus whatever gear you need at the Dumbo node to ship your best work.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>Full coverage:</strong> Premium health, dental, and vision insurance (US).</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>4 weeks vacation:</strong> We want you to actually take 4 weeks off every year to recharge.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>New parents:</strong> 4 months of fully paid parental leave for new additions to your family.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>Retreats:</strong> Regular team events and offsites to sync on the road ahead.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>No Deadlines:</strong> We don't ship to satisfy a calendar; we ship to satisfy our creators.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>Open Source:</strong> Our code is public. You can read the <a href="https://github.com/antiwork/gumroad" class="underline hover:text-pink">repo</a> before you even apply.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">How to apply</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-4 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>Email us.</strong> Send a few sentences about your origin story to <a href="mailto:jobs@antiwork.com" class="underline hover:text-pink">jobs@antiwork.com</a>.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>Proof of work.</strong> Include a list of things you've built (with URLs). If you want to skip the line, find an open issue in our <a href="https://github.com/antiwork/gumroad" class="underline hover:text-pink">GitHub repo</a>, fix it, and send the PR.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>The Sync.</strong> If the work is good, we'll do a quick call to see if our Dumbo node is a fit.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><strong>The Trial.</strong> 4â€“6 week-long paid work trial. You ship real code to real creators. If you're a builder, you stay.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="px-8 pb-16 lg:px-[4vw] lg:pb-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:gap-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto items-center">
      <h1 class="font-medium text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-center">Not looking for a full-time role? Help us build in public.</h1>
      <%= render "home/shared/button", text: "Contribute on GitHub", url: "https://github.com/antiwork/gumroad" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= image_tag "about/new-sale.svg", alt: "Gumroad illustration", class: "w-full min-h-[300px] object-cover" %>

  <%= render "home/shared/footer" %>
</div>

